snippet.title: Hearts of Oak
snippet.description:
GUEST INTERVIEWS - Monday and Thursday 8pm
WEEKLY NEWS REVIEW - Saturday 8pm

Our Children | Our Country | Our Future | Our Freedom
Hearts of Oak is a populist Free Speech alliance that seeks to push back the cultural Marxism that pervades all areas of our society.
Free speech, religious disagreement, children's rights and an open and free discussion on any topic are bedrocks to a democratic free society and we seek to promote and champion these basic rights.
Sign up for our weekly Email at 
https://heartsofoak.org/
For all our links go to 
https://heartsofoak.org/find-us/
